        <h5 class="card-title">Why use SAFE Team?</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>Free rides for USF students</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>Fast, convenient transportation</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>Improved safety during nighttime hours</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>Easy online booking system</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="my-5">

<div class="row g-4">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card h-100">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-user-shield fa-3x text-success mb-3"></i>
        <h5 class="card-title">Enhanced Safety</h5>
        <p class="card-text">SAFE Team provides a secure transportation option for students during nighttime hours, reducing the need to walk alone on campus.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card h-100">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt fa-3x text-success mb-3"></i>
        <h5 class="card-title">Easy to Use</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Simply log in with your USF credentials, request a ride, and track your driver in real-time. No phone calls needed!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card h-100">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-clock fa-3x text-success mb-3"></i>
        <h5 class="card-title">Quick & Reliable</h5>
        <p class="card-text">View estimated wait times, receive notifications, and enjoy a swift ride to your destination on campus.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>